rawDocument.description:
I'm looking for an experienced Angular developer to create a web-based dashboard application. This dashboard will primarily display user activity data, so a strong understanding of user analytics will be necessary. 

Key Responsibilities:
- Design and develop an interactive, user-friendly dashboard using Angular.
- Implement features to analyze user activity data effectively.

Ideal Skills:
- Proficiency in Angular and web application development.
- Prior experience in creating dashboard applications.
- Strong understanding of user analytics.

This project requires a keen eye for detail and a commitment to delivering a high-quality, functional application.

Looking for a long term development for Web Based Application.
